{"tid":1415761,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲要唔要「民意」？不妨一齊諗諗何謂民意","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T17:02:38.000Z","uid":39021,"like":90,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"40a819404f6759804bde6b1f51069e0a72842bca","tid":1415761,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:08:26.000Z","msg":"利申：今日發白日夢食完煙黎，放火都絕不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到好多巴絲話唔需要再理「民意」，但究竟「民意」係乜？<br />\n身為一個唔中唔青嘅打工仔，我見到嘅「民意」係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔敢上前又唔敢罷工嘅中產瘋狂買物資比前線（見過有人捐二十對6092X，靜靜雞搵細路幫手散貨）<br />\n2. 公眾場合有廢老屌後生仔時，市民立即以道理反擊<br />\n3. 默許子女做前線既父母<br />\n4. 冒風險開門放義士入場既實Q<br />\n5. 堅持支持義士既商戶同車長<br />\n6. 罷工時願意喺訪問講正面說話既平民<br />\n7. 連聲都唔出得嘅上流人士用自己方法保護大家（好多時大家係睇唔到，因為唔揚得出去）<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得唔需要「民意」的話，我可以跟<br />\n但請唔好忘記可以走到呢一日，都係因為一直有呢班「民意」暗中支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789f9556425f87eef6fa5615ae415a50124a5788","tid":1415761,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5522bc892c78349a48142886b69a7beafe63b8","tid":1415761,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:10:52.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c6476e3064122506f1c2dc6bddd8e243eef182b6","tid":1415761,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:11:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0fd13c6e6015b5ff24c9e751c27eb18dcce6db22","tid":1415761,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:12:13.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"909811d92cae13f6df89a10f8badbe0f95e561d1","tid":1415761,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:13:54.000Z","msg":"雖然自推好柒，但我呢個post係非常真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji